  "subject": "fix issue vnfrqts-264",
  "commit_message": "fix issue vnfrqts-264\n\nSpecific requirements for using the new mechanism to transfer\nperiodic performance measurements for PNFs/VNFs implementing\n3GPP network functions (e g RAN). When using the bulk transmission\nmechanism to transfer bulk monitoring data to ONAP/DCAE to\nsupport 5G/PNF, the 3GPP format should be supported.\n\nIssue-ID: VNFRQTS-264\nSigned-off-by: zu, qiang <qiang.zu@gmail.com>\nChange-Id: I4968bd2ad7273bbbfd8938f64aa5a2af437a333a\n",
